                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-767" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM JONES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Smith, pawnbroker, of South-street, Marylebone—I produce a coat, two scarfs, a handkerchief, and a dessert-fork—some of these duplicates found in the prisoner's box are what I gave.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
