                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-768" type="given" value="FREDERICK"></interp>FREDERICK COLLINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Thompson, a pawnbroker. I produce three pairs of Wellington boots and two waistcoats, pawned by the Prisoner, I believe, the boots on the 20th Sept., in the name of John Smith, the waistcoat and handkerchiefs on the 3rd Oct.—I find the corresponding duplicates here.</p>
